headline: Henry Schein to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conference in March
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., March 03, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC), the world’s largest provider of health care solutions to office-based dental and medical practitioners, announced today that the Company will present at the Leerink Global Healthcare Conference on Tuesday, March 11th, 2025, at the W South Beach hotel in Miami at 1:40 p.m. Eastern time.
